once a pon a time, In a forest far away. There lived a monkey who deicded to live on a berry tree. which was near the banks of the river. In that same forest, There lived a crocodile and his wife...
the crocodile one day came to the banks of the river and lay, Resting under the tree.After seeing the large crocodile with no food, The monkey felt bad for him so the kind hearted monkey offerd him some fruits